title: QuickBooks 2009 Update to R6 [ ii ]
description:
If you need a safe way to run your business with Quickbooks and are afraid to turn on autoupdates because there is a good chance someday your version gets ruined with a patch push...

I have done the legwork for you.  I have downloaded and tested this file with Beast's great work with the Quickbooks 2009 Hack.

Works wonderful, even one month after still using it. Enjoy
